<div class="section white">
  <div class="row container">
    <h2 class="header">Saving has never been easier</h2>
    <p class="grey-text text-darken-3 lighten-3">Ever found yourself having too much month at the end of your money? If you do then Cache is the perfect saving plan for you! And if you don't find yourself in that predicament...Cache is still the perfect
      saving plan for you as well! Who wouldn't like having more cash and attractive awards on the side?!</p>
    <p>So you wanna find out more about Cache! Not to worry we got your back.</p>
    <p>Think of Cache as a digital floating cloud piggy bank. Just deposit a portion of your monthly income and get awesome stuff (ranging from cash back and even discounts from retailers!) from just saving money in your digital cloud pig! (lets call it
      'Hamlet')
      <i class="em em-pig"></i>
      For every $100 you deposit you get back $1, 25% of that $1 ($0.25) would be cash, where you can spend anywhere or you could save it too. The other 75% of that $1 ($0.75) would be pooled into your Cache reward balance, where it can be converted into
      discount or promotion for our retail partners!</p>
    <p>Getting too confusing? Do not fret, below is a little break down as to how this saving works and how much stand to earn!</p>
