    <p>At the end of the year you will be getting back $864 worth of stuff just for saving $7,200. Now thats a pretty decent deal, you're happy and so is Hamlet. Out of the $864, you get $216 in cash and $648 worth of Cache rewards! These rewards ranges
      from discounts at eateries or at boutiques.</p>

